  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_3_397-428",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "397-428",
      "markText": "既然人的性格是由环境造成的，那就必须使环境成为合乎人性的环境。",
      "totalCount": 990,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=397&rangeEnd=428",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=397&rangeEnd=428"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_4_1789-1801",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1789-1801",
      "markText": "由此可证，世界并不完美。",
      "totalCount": 266,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1789&rangeEnd=1801",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1789&rangeEnd=1801"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_4_1409-1430",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1409-1430",
      "markText": "这种沉默我们可称之为普适性同义词或者全能词",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1409&rangeEnd=1430",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1409&rangeEnd=1430"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_26_8494-8535",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "8494-8535",
      "markText": "然后一个女人说：“以前我们只是东西，因此别无选择。以后，人再也不会被当作东西了。”",
      "totalCount": 200,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=8494&rangeEnd=8535",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=8494&rangeEnd=8535"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_4_3601-3624",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3601-3624",
      "markText": "综上所述，我们便可由此评估蛀虫侵蚀的困难程度。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3601&rangeEnd=3624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3601&rangeEnd=3624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_6_9265-9424",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9265-9424",
      "markText": "告诉我，这个九月怎么样？这样的天气我们已经久违了。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9265&rangeEnd=9424",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9265&rangeEnd=9424"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_5_740-836",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "740-836",
      "markText": "罪行肯定无法遭到惩罚了，因为受害者噤声无言，也因为调查人员草率敷衍——要等到椅子彻底倒下，等到这场眼下尚不足以致命的跌倒彻底完成时，调查人员才会例行公事，去瞅瞅椅子腿是否曾被歹毒或蓄意地破坏。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=740&rangeEnd=836",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=740&rangeEnd=836"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_4_3284-3305",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3284-3305",
      "markText": "不必在此处多费口舌了。不过再多说一句也无妨",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3284&rangeEnd=3305",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3284&rangeEnd=3305"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_4_1920-1933",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1920-1933",
      "markText": "变的是时代，不变的是时间。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1920&rangeEnd=1933",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1920&rangeEnd=1933"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_4_1321-1378",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1321-1378",
      "markText": "假如词语的意思都是相同的，假如词语都能根据相同词源归类，那么生活就会简单得多，只需缩略缩略再缩略，直到变为拟声词；",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1321&rangeEnd=1378",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1321&rangeEnd=1378"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_4_1000-1025",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1000-1025",
      "markText": "因为“倒塌”这个词在葡萄牙语中的字面意思是边缘掉落",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1000&rangeEnd=1025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1000&rangeEnd=1025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_11_543-592",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "543-592",
      "markText": "他下令无论腐烂程度如何，全国所有坟地里的尸骨都必须清出来，一具具装进新棺材，然后运去那座公墓埋葬。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=543&rangeEnd=592",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=543&rangeEnd=592"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_5_5820-5883",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5820-5883",
      "markText": "不过为了打发时间，还是多说两句吧，因为老人出于长久以来各种各样的原因，对自己的人性产生了怀疑。可是，这会儿他依然像人一样坐着。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5820&rangeEnd=5883",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5820&rangeEnd=5883"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_5_1137-1318",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1137-1318",
      "markText": "也不知其间经过了多少年，不过考虑到鞘翅目昆虫的短暂寿命，可以审慎断言的是，在那荣耀之日到来以前，它的子孙世代必然长年累月地以这块桃花心木为食，多么高贵的种族，多么英勇的国度啊！",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300113132&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1137&rangeEnd=1318",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/806327c0813ab92b1g012235?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1137&rangeEnd=1318"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300113132_9_3310-3397",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3310-3397",
      "markText": "他摸索着打开车门，想从车内的窒息中解脱出来，就在做出这个动作的同时，或许因为他快死了，或许因为发动机已经坏了，总之他的身体歪向左侧，滑出了汽车，又滑远了些，最后横在石头路上。",
